        <para>
          <text>Section 24(5): insert <amend.in quote="1"><changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">205 to 210F, 221,</citation></changeable></amend.in> after <quote.in quote="1">204, </quote.in>.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Section 24A(3): omit <amend.in quote="1">215 to 218</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1"><changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">205 to 205S, 207 to 207P</citation></changeable> (so far as they are applicable to candidate donations), <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">209 to 209E</citation></changeable>, 215 to <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">219, 221</citation></changeable></amend.in>.</text>
        </para>
        <head5 id="DLM1833727" toc="yes">
          <heading>Summary Proceedings Act 1957 (1957 No 87)</heading>
        </head5>
        <para>
          <text>Part 2 of Schedule 1: insert the following item after the item relating to section 218 of the Electoral Act 1993:</text>
          <table align="center" fontsize="9.5" frame="none" id="DLM1833728" leading="11.5">
